{"tid":1489114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【文宣請入，重要】「解放軍入城」傳言只會令外媒問錯問題","createTime":"2019-08-19T19:55:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T06:18:04.000Z","uid":59815,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"08add42f24ad3847fe713acf1d5c7a8bf1792234","tid":1489114,"uid":59815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T19:55:30.000Z","msg":"「解放軍入城」，正常香港人都知短期內唔會發生。民間記者會一句「返屋企瞓覺」幽默回應，成個「恐怖霧霾」無曬。<br />\n<br />\n中共未會出軍隊，因為根本唔使。洗腦黑警加黑社會刀手周街劈，個武力程度已經夠高。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁點解匪國重要吹依個風？其實係為左掩護警暴升級。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n吹左風之後，人人問：解放軍來了，怎麼辦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母講撚到解放軍未來，就未死得人咁！其實黑警暴力已經日日升級，但由於「解放軍無入城」，變左警黑暴力無咁顯見，好似解放軍先有武力咁！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n參考：黃之鋒同民陣mk仔都話外媒係咁問<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CBA2CLm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCBA2CLm.png&h=152fba94&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RO5J6DG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRO5J6DG.png&h=091d9c97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁點拆？<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">將焦點放返警暴、爆眼少女、黑社會斬人，全部入中共數，話俾人聽，係港澳辦號召黑警同黑社會對付黎民！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n將港澳辦記者會同警暴、各界人士（黑社會）並列，講出中共無派軍，派的是警黑，而它不是比解放軍弱很多的事情！"},{"pid":"bbfcd7457ba2f24150d22ebae986dbb19100efea","tid":1489114,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy